data.title: About: WVVW
data.meta_description: WVVW-LP was a Progressive Southern Gospel formatted broadcast radio station licensed to Belpre, Ohio, serving Parkersburg, West Virginia. WVVW-LP was owned and operated by Fellowship Baptist Church and Ministries. The licensee surrendered WVVW-LP's license to the Federal Communications Commission (FCC) on July 27, 2017, who cancelled it the same day.
